Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I woke up and Twitter had taken my account.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.51,0:00:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No reason given.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.25,0:00:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I can't code.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}9 years in crypto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.76,0:00:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}AI trades my thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.89,0:00:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.90,0:00:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The moment it happened, I realized every thread I'd written, every follower, every receipt I'd posted — all of it, held by one platform that didn't call first.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.78,0:00:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Same day I did something that sounded unrelated — I launched bilingual mode on my own website.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}At the time it felt small.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.53,0:00:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The week I had nowhere else to speak, it stopped feeling small.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.78,0:00:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}There's a sentence I'd heard for years and always dismissed as cheesy — don't build your most valuable thing on top of ground you don't own.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That day, that sentence became an invoice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}From Day 10 on — my own site is home base.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.62,0:00:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Every other platform is just distribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.80,0:01:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The kind that can be turned off at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.90,0:01:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 11 tomorrow — I wrote the full story of Trade number 267.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.07,0:01:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Follow along.
